Package service

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Service
    Interface of all methods that the user interface requires in order to interact with the database and object model
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractService
    Service that implements all read-only methods (this is because for testing, there must be a way to isolate the database from the testing yet still test the service.
    DefaultService
    Provides a way for the user interface to interact with the object model and the database.
    InMemoryService
    A concrete Service that could be instantiated to test the service methods that are non-database related.
    Population<PersonType extends Person>
    A Binary Search Tree that holds nodes that are children of the Person object.
    ScriptRunner
    Tool to run database scripts

    Stores ways to compare students in the form of comparators (e.g.
